article.headline: McNeese St. 64, Florida Atlantic 59
article.story: BOCA RATON, Fla. (AP) -- John Pichon scored 15 points as McNeese State beat Florida Atlantic 64-59 on Saturday night. Diego Kapelan and Jarvis Bradley both had 11 points for McNeese St. (3-3), and John Ford added 10. Ford and Kleon Penn each had seven rebounds for the Cowboys, and Bradley pulled down six. McNeese St. outrebounded Florida Atlantic 43-33. Penn also blocked eight shots. Carlos Monroe scored 21 points for Florida Atlantic (1-7), and Jeff Parmer and Xavier Perkins each had 10.
